---
title: Spicy Sichuan Chicken & Green Bean Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This easy meal showcases tender chicken strips with bold Sichuan garlic paste, sriracha, honey and soy, delivering savoury, sweet and hot all in one bite. Paired with aromatic garlic rice, this flavour-packed dish is perfect for a a Calorie Smart weeknight dinner or a special treat!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
